IC.SymbolTable

Class SymbolTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • IC.SymbolTable.SymbolTable

  • public class SymbolTable
extends java.lang.Object
    A SymbolTable object hold a symbol table or a scope in the program compiling process.

    Asaf Bruner, Aviv Goll
